


g_margin(1)                    Scilab Function                    g_margin(1)






NAME
  g_margin - gain margin

CALLING SEQUENCE
  [gm [,fr])=g_margin(h)

PARAMETERS

  h    : syslin list representing a linear system in state-space or transfer
       form

DESCRIPTION
  returns gm, the gain margin (dB) of h (SISO plant) and fr, the achieved
  corresponding frequency.

SEE ALSO
  p_margin, black, chart







































